@{b}  RELEASE 7@{ub} (18.08.99)
  ---------
   Documentation is now in AmigaGuide format.

   Many icons have been renamed to better names,
   so if you already have OpusNIbar installed I
   recommend you to delete the old pack before
   Installing this pack. Or else you will get
   duplicates of some icons.

  10 New Images Added:

   · Arexx
   · Cinema4D
   · Find 3
   · Home
   · MagicHat
   · QuickTime
   · Reload
   · Soccer
   · Sound
   · YingYang



